                    "value": 1
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> The famliar shadow hit a living creature it is duplicating with a shadow hand Strike on its previous action</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The famliar shadow pulls at the target's shadow, making the creature @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Enfeebled]{Enfeebled 1}. This is cumulative with other enfeebled conditions from shadows, to a maximum of @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Enfeebled]{Enfeebled 4}. If this increases a creature's enfeebled value to 3 or more, the target's shadow is separated from its body (see shadow spawn). The enfeebled value from Steal Shadow decreases by 1 every hour.</p>"
                },
